graphics.name: Tropane, piperidine and pyridine alkaloid biosynthesis

nodes.name: glycerone phosphate:iminosuccinate alkyltransferase (cyclizing)

nodes.name: 6-hydroxynicotinate,NADH:oxygen oxidoreductase (3-hydroxylating, decarboxylating)

nodes.name: Deamido-NAD+:L-glutamine amido-ligase (AMP-forming)

nodes.name: 5-phospho-alpha-D-ribose 1-diphosphate:nicotinate ligase (ADP, diphosphate-forming)

nodes.name: Aldehyde:oxygen oxidoreductase

nodes.name: Aldehyde:oxygen oxidoreductase

nodes.name: NAD+ + Histone N6-acetyl-L-lysine + H2O <=> Nicotinamide + Histone-L-lysine + O-Acetyl-ADP-ribose + H+
